message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper involves the use of deep learning to digitally stain optical coherence tomography images, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper focuses on medical imaging and glaucoma management, which could also place it in the medical imaging (cs.MED) and neuroscience (cs.NEURON) sub-categories.
